Inspect rendered gateway policy for an MCP server

Usage:
  mcp-runtime server policy [command]

Available Commands:
  inspect     Show the rendered gateway policy document for a server

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for policy

Global Flags:
      --debug      Enable debug mode with structured error logging
      --use-kube   Use direct Kubernetes mode with kubectl; requires admin/operator cluster access (admin/dev/test only)

Use "mcp-runtime server policy [command] --help" for more information about a command.
